items.name: Iot-based-leakage-current-detector-
items.description: This paper presents an IoT-based solution for detecting leakage currents in electrical systems, which can pose risks like shocks and fires. The system uses sensors to monitor electrical circuits in real-time, detecting abnormal currents and alerting users via a cloud platform. It enhances safety by enabling immediate response to potential hazards.
